Yes...

30
00:05:04,000  -->  00:05:05,400
So...

31
00:05:07,500  -->  00:05:09,000
How can I turn these off?

32
00:05:11,900  -->  00:05:13,600
You have to find a reference

33
00:05:45,700  -->  00:05:48,200
to a ServiceContext.

34
00:05:53,100  -->  00:05:54,500
And then?

35
00:05:50,400  -->  00:05:52,000
Use method
getServiceContentHandlers()

36
00:05:53,300  -->  00:05:54,500
