are on

42
00:08:59,100  -->  00:09:00,600
You can call
isSubtitlingOn

43
00:09:10,300  -->  00:09:13,100
or you can call
listAvailableLanguages()

44
00:09:14,600  -->  00:09:16,300
Oh, I see.

45
00:10:32,400  -->  00:10:34,000
