subtitles?

46
00:10:35,000  -->  00:10:36,400
You can call setSubtitling

47
00:10:55,400  -->  00:10:57,000
Use boolean value to
set it on or off

48
00:11:01,600  -->  00:11:06,300
You know, true if you want
them on

49
00:11:07,900  -->  00:11:09,600
and false, if you
want them off.

50
00:11:10,100  -->  00:11:15,400
Okay.
I have to try that.

51
00:11:17,500  -->  00:11:19,400
